title: Danish Demining Group,DDG,Mine clearance 2013/2014
description: Through demining, training and capacity development Danish Demining Group, DDG, aims their phase out project 2013/2014 to improve the humanitarian situation of the poorest region in Basra, southern Iraq, as well as contribute to socio-economic development. DDG will continue the impact-led and community focused approach initiated in 2010, which was supported by Sida.
